      • yearMillis

        public static long yearMillis​(int year,
                              boolean leap)
        Calculated start of year in millis. For example of year 2008 this is equivalent to parsing "2008-01-01T00:00:00.000Z", except this method is faster.
        Parameters:
        year - the year
        leap - true if give year is leap year
        Returns:
        millis for start of year.
